strings:
<voice_0x01001307><se_low>Marta: Dobroe utro. Good morning.
So you have found my herb garden.

<voice_0x01001308><se_low>Marta: This cave is just the right temperature and humidity for them. And it is the only place
I can grow my nook grass.
<voice_0x01001309><se_low>Marta: Beyond those iron bars is the ruin I told you about. I usually keep it locked.
<voice_0x0100130A><se_low>Marta: It is a very special place, so I cannot allow visitors inside. Forgive me.
